column4: Little interest or pleasure in doing things.
column6: Feeling nervous; anxious or on edge.
column7: Not being able to stop or control worrying.
column8: In the last month; how often have you felt that you were unable to control the important things in your life?
column9: In the last month; how often have you felt confident about your ability to handle your personal problems?
column10: In the last month; how often have you felt that things were going your way?
column11: In the last month; how often have you been able to control irritations in your life?
column12: In the last month; how often have you felt that you were on top of things?
column13: In the last month; how often have you been angered because of things that were outside of your control?
column14: In the last month; how often have you felt difficulties were piling up so high that you could not overcome them?
